##############################################################################
#  URFD Blacklist
#
#  One callsign per line. Blacklisted callsigns are denied access.
#  Supports wildcard (*) as the last character.
#  An empty file means nobody is blocked.
#
#  Examples:
#    *       deny access to everybody (not recommended)
#    LX*     deny all callsigns starting with LX
#    LX3JL   deny LX3JL exactly
#
##############################################################################
